289
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:14,620
Right. Xuan Xuan is right.

290
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:19,140
Uncle, mommy is really good.

291
00:21:19,140 --> 00:21:21,490
I really love mommy.

292
00:21:21,490 --> 00:21:26,310
But I agreed to give mommy to you.

293
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:34,640
So I really need you to treat mommy really, really well.

294
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:37,540
Of course. I promise you

295
00:21:37,540 --> 00:21:41,060
