296
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:44,180
Uncle, you're so handsome!

297
00:21:44,180 --> 00:21:45,630
Good girl.

298
00:21:45,630 --> 00:21:46,960
Haoyu.

299
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:48,460
