338
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:24,980
Wrote me letters to criticize me and then would ask me to write him back with self-reflections.

339
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:26,710
Qi Sile.

340
00:24:26,710 --> 00:24:30,610
It's only because you care about each other, that’s why you fight. Do you understand?

341
00:24:32,860 --> 00:24:36,710
What went on between me and him isn't easy to explain.

342
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:45,510
My dear daughter.

343
00:24:45,510 --> 00:24:48,280
When you were born,

344
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:50,260
I would look at you,

345
00:24:50,260 --> 00:24:53,670
thinking, how long would it take,

346
00:24:53,670 --> 00:24:56,910
for such a small body to be fully grown?

347
00:24:56,910 --> 00:24:59,320
I believe a lot of fathers are just like me,

348
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:01,280
shamelessly imagining

349
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:05,410
whether you’ll become a scientist when you grow up

350
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:08,840
or an astronaut.

351
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:14,820
But later on, I didn’t want to you to grow up.

352
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:16,680
I would think about how one day

353
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:19,710
you'd become a lady and get married,

354
00:25:19,710 --> 00:25:21,780
you would no longer grab my thumb and ask me

355
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:25,550
this or that or ride on my shoulders out and about.

356
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:28,330
Just thinking of that,

357
00:25:28,330 --> 00:25:31,260
makes my heart feel empty.

358
00:25:31,980 --> 00:25:34,140
When you were five years old,

359
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:39,550
I got injured in the forest at work and was bedridden for several years.

360
00:25:39,550 --> 00:25:44,200
Your mother became the only source of income for the family.

361
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:47,070
Sile, that’s why

362
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:48,950
